{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2089222, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406622, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "半决赛之后选手A被B的粉丝狂喷，A说自己抽中忠臣本来就应该盲狙。", "timestamp": 1626585768, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089223, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406622, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "粉丝喷A的其中一个理由是A作为忠臣不应该选黄盖。", "timestamp": 1626585809, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089378, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406622, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感觉这个有点像之前篮球赛的的瓜？都是赛制导致获得最好成绩的最优策略并非为在游戏本身中获胜的最优策略", "timestamp": 1626587787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089391, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 406622, "reply_to": 2089223, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 可选的将池是啥才能决定要不要选黄盖？", "timestamp": 1626587978, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089480, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 406622, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "比赛的目的就是晋级呀。", "timestamp": 1626589349, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089485, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 406622, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "假如杀主公能让我晋级，那就去杀主公。就这样。", "timestamp": 1626589446, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089494, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 406622, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为了晋级，或者在输了也保证能晋级的情况下假如输掉比赛能在决赛遇上不太强的对手，那就去输。", "timestamp": 1626589620, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 406622, "reply": 7, "tag": null, "text": "在三国杀老炮杯(身份场)半决赛中，某职业选手A在最后一局之前排名第三，并在最后一局抽到二号位忠臣身份。A为了保住自己的晋级资格(前三名)，直接选黄盖并将三号位的选手B(当前排名第四的选手)打成一血。这个行为你能接受吗？", "timestamp": 1626585592, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626589619, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"能": 38, "不能": 11, "三国杀是什么": 20}, "vote_options": ["能", "不